title: cra_soc
text:
This is the first section of the CRA SOC.

library(shinylive)

Warning: package 'shinylive' was built under R version 4.4.3


#| '!! shinylive warning !!': |
#|   shinylive does not work in self-contained HTML documents.
#|   Please set `embed-resources: false` in your metadata.
#| standalone: true
#| viewerHeight: 500
library(shiny)
ui <- fluidPage(
  sliderInput("obs", "Observations:", 10, 200, 100),
  plotOutput("plot")
)
server <- function(input, output, session) {
  output$plot <- renderPlot({
    hist(rnorm(input$obs))
  })
}
shinyApp(ui, server)
